
sequenceDiagram
    participant S as Stopwatch
    participant H as History
    participant U as UI
    U->>S: start()
    S-->>U: time updates
    U->>S: stop()
    S-->>U: return elapsed time
    U->>H: add_record(time)
    U->>S: reset()
    U->>H: get_records()
    H-->>U: return records
